GUIDELINES   Audience: Registered UIC students  A reserved room/classroom (quiet with no through traffic)  A dedicated audience of UIC students (students who are regularly convened to attend an organizational meeting or class session)  Required audience size:12 students or more  Technology in the room: laptop, screen, and data projector       Workshop Request    Disclaimer * Required  Yes, I understand I have read the above "Important" information about the workshop request and the other resources before submitting this form. I understand that as a requestor I am responsible for reserving a room with technological equipment such as a projector, a screen, and a laptop/computer linked to the projector. 

